  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Space Tormentor is a Shoot'Em Up Bullet Hell Game in which You immerse Yourself as an lonely pilot with mission to destroy as many alien enemies as it's possible. You have been traped and sent to unknown sector of galaxy.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Your goal is to fight your way back to Earth.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>There are two types of game modes:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>First one is Story Mode divided to 3 stages with 30 Levels and the second one is Death Wave in which You try to destroy a large hordes of aliens to survive.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Features:</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Power Ups to enchance your spaceship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Letters from destroyed enemies to get SPACE TORMENTOR caption to unlock your special ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Your EMP ability to temporarily disarm your enemies or your cloak ability to fool them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more aggresive you play, the better chance of survival you have</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some enemies have other behaviours so fight your way to victory wisely and quickly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/599e3b69e89d9a76678a3949e6e3428c.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/355ccb86cfc0100d88b15e65d4bd88c1.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/0be09dafe946916824269f636e527b6b.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Space Tormentor is a Shoot'Em Up Bullet Hell Game in which You immerse Yourself as an lonely pilot with mission to destroy as many alien enemies as it's possible. You have been traped and sent to unknown sector of galaxy.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Your goal is to fight your way back to Earth.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>There are two types of game modes:</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>First one is Story Mode divided to 3 stages with 30 Levels and the second one is Death Wave in which You try to destroy a large hordes of aliens to survive.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Features:</i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Power Ups to enchance your spaceship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Letters from destroyed enemies to get SPACE TORMENTOR caption to unlock your special ability</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Your EMP ability to temporarily disarm your enemies or your cloak ability to fool them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more aggresive you play, the better chance of survival you have</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some enemies have other behaviours so fight your way to victory wisely and quickly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/599e3b69e89d9a76678a3949e6e3428c.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/355ccb86cfc0100d88b15e65d4bd88c1.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4482360/extras/0be09dafe946916824269f636e527b6b.avif?t=1773833689\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
